1. *Ocem* da idem u školu. (I want to go to school.)
2. *Ocem* da se upoznamo. (I want us to get acquainted.)
3. *Oceo* mi je da budem srećan. (My father told me to be happy.)
4. *Ocem* da ti pomognem. (I want to help you.)
5. *Oce* mi da se dobro zabavim. (My father told me to have a good time.)
6. *Oceo* mi je da učim strani jezik. (My father told me to learn a foreign language.)
7. *Ocem* da imamo srećan život. (I want us to have a happy life.)
8. *Ocem* da čitam knjige. (I want to read books.)